# Archetype Project Rules

## Project Overview
This is the Archetype project. The project primarily runs on **https://archetype.elghareeb.space** in production.

## Build and Run Commands

### just Commands
The project uses a `justfile` (https://github.com/casey/just) in the
`infrastructure/` directory. Run `just` (or `just --list`) to see the full,
self-documenting list. The common ones:

- `just up` / `just up-bg` - Start all services (foreground / detached)
- `just down` - Stop all services (volumes/data kept)
- `just down-volumes` - Stop AND delete volumes (DESTROYS the database)
- `just restart` / `just restart-api` - Restart everything / just the api
- `just logs` - Follow logs for all services
- `just ps` - Show service status
- `just migrate` - Run database migrations
- `just reindex` - Rebuild all Meilisearch indexes from the DB (schema + documents)
- `just setup-search-indexes` / `just sync-all-search-indexes` - Index schema only / sync data
- `just celery_status` - Inspect active Celery workers
- `just backup` - Take a one-off gzipped pg_dump into `./backups/`
- `just postgres-version` / `just postgres-upgrade-17-to-18` - PostgreSQL version / major upgrade
- `just certbot` - Obtain/renew Let's Encrypt certificates

**Note:** Run just recipes from the `infrastructure/` directory (or pass
`--justfile infrastructure/justfile --working-directory infrastructure` from elsewhere).

### Docker Compose
The project uses **Docker Compose** as the primary method for running the application. The `compose.yaml` file is located in the `infrastructure/` directory.

Key services:
- `api` - Django backend API (image pulled from ghcr.io/archetype-pal/backend)
- `frontend` - Next.js frontend (image pulled from ghcr.io/archetype-pal/frontend)
- `postgres` - PostgreSQL 18 database
- `meilisearch` - Search engine (replaced Elasticsearch)
- `redis` - Cache and Celery message broker
- `celery` - Background task worker
- `nginx` - Web server and reverse proxy (TLS termination)
- `image_server` - Sipi IIIF image server
- `certbot` - Let's Encrypt certificate issuance/renewal
- `pg_backup` - Periodic logical pg_dump sidecar (see docs/backup-runbook.md)

## Development Workflow
- Use `docker compose` commands (or the justfile) from the `infrastructure/` directory.
- The justfile provides convenient shortcuts for common operations; `just --list` shows them.
- Production URL: https://archetype.elghareeb.space

## Project Structure
- `api/` - Django backend application
- `frontend/` - Next.js frontend application
- `infrastructure/` - Docker Compose configuration, nginx config, Sipi config, and the justfile
- `site-gh/` - GitHub Pages site/documentation
